---
title: "Gallery"
description: "A look at Coach Osama's training, nutrition and program highlights."
---

<section class="grid-bg">
  <div class="container-x py-16 sm:py-20">
    <p class="section-kicker">Gallery</p>
    <h1 class="section-title mb-4">Behind the scenes.</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-brand-off/70 max-w-2xl">
      A glimpse into our programs, meals and training moments.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container-x grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
    {% for img in gallery.images %}
      <figure class="card p-2 overflow-hidden">
        <img src="{{ img.src }}" alt="{{ img.alt_en }}" loading="lazy"
             class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-xl">
      </figure>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
